  "clinicalPearl": "Pneumothorax is an ACUTE PRESSURE LOSS + LUNG COLLAPSE EMERGENCY. The triad of hyperresonance, absent breath sounds, and tracheal deviation demands immediate decompression before imaging. Never wait for CXR in tension pneumothorax."
